## Edge Detection
Run the code in 'evaluateSegmentation.m'. 

'nonmax.m' instead of Canny edge detection is used. 

## Image Segmentation
Just run the code in 'segmentMain.m'. It will get the segmentation results of image 'gumballs.jpg', 'snake.jpg', 'twins.jpg' and 'coins.jpg'. Previous results are stored in the 'result' directory. 

Some parameters can be set in 'segmentMain.m': k_textons, winSize, numColorRegions, numTextureRegions. 